  • Overview

    Designer finishesRiverfront parkSpectacular sweeping viewsWhole foodsAbundant natural light throughoutCommons parkCustomized kitchen
    Perfectly poised in the heart of Riverfront Park, this stunning, updated and upgraded residence has everything you’re looking for in Luxury, Lifestyle and Location. Overlooking Commons Park with views of Longs Peak the expansive open floor plan boasts walls of windows, spectacular sweeping views and abundant natural light throughout. The customized kitchen and living areas are thoughtfully designed and perfect for entertaining. Relax in the king-size Primary Suite with spa-like custom designer finishes. A secondary king-size bedroom overlooks the park, and a 3rd non-conforming bedroom (no window) is perfect for a guest room, home office or media room. Colorado evenings can be enjoyed from two separate outdoor spaces. The private terrace overlooks Commons Park to the West and has a gas line perfect for BBQ’ing and entertaining outdoors. This chic and sophisticated residence captures the best of the exceptional resort-like neighborhood lifestyle of Riverfront Park. In this incomparable and coveted location in downtown Denver on Commons Park, you can garage your cars and enjoy the walkability to Union Station, Whole Foods, all of downtown Denver’s sports and entertainment venues, restaurants, museums, the Denver Center for Performing Arts and ride/walk endless miles of trails on the Cherry Creek Bike Path and beyond.
